title: Trump Takes Credit for Kevin McCarthy Dropping Out of Race for Speaker of the House – Video 10/8/15 | Tea Party
text:
(Before It's News)
Here is Donald Trump in Last Vegas yesterday taking some credit for Kevin McCarthy dropping out of the race to become the next Speaker of the House.
“They’re giving me a lot of credit for that because I said, ‘You need somebody very, very tough and very smart. . . .’”
